    "collapsible_content_WK36AG": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_wcnJBJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the Silver Snoopy Award?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>NASA's Silver Snoopy Award has been presented since 1968 to those who contributed to human spaceflight safety. Snoopy was NASA's safety mascot — a symbol of mission vigilance. OMEGA received the award in 1970 for the Speedmaster's role in the Apollo 13 rescue.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_VTtbRD": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the automatic movement work?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>The movement self-winds through the natural motion of your wrist — no battery required. If it's been sitting for a few days, wind it manually by turning the crown 20-30 times before wearing.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_EhacPx": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes this watch special?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Every detail is a tribute to NASA's Apollo era — the silver dial echoes the original Snoopy Award pin, the blue accents mirror the mission colour scheme, and the caseback pays homage to Apollo 13. It's a piece of space history you can wear.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_kDzQWe": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What does the warranty cover?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Full 2-year warranty on all manufacturing defects. Plus a 30-day no-questions money-back guarantee. We stand behind every watch we ship.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_WnRgiU": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How fast does it ship?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Orders dispatch within 1-2 business days. Express worldwide delivery in 5-7 business days. Every shipment tracked and insured from our facility to your door.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
